# =============================================================================
# PUBLIC REPO: genomic data and secrets must NEVER be committed.
# The real-genome cohorts (Uganda Genome Resource, Peruvian Genome Project,
# Corpas family) are controlled-access / personal data. Reviewers reproduce by
# obtaining them through the routes in real-genome-arm/DATA-ACCESS.md.
# =============================================================================
*.vcf
*.vcf.gz
*.vcf.gz.tbi
*.vcf.bgz
*.vcf.bgz.tbi
*.bcf
*.bed
*.bim
*.fam
*.bam
*.cram
*.crai
*.bai
*.tar.gz
*.tgz
# keep the small config region BED (coordinates only, not genotype data)
!real-genome-arm/config/*.bed
# reference genomes / phasing panels (large; fetch separately)
*.fa
*.fa.gz
*.fna
*.fna.gz
*.fna.bgz
*.chain
*.chain.gz
pypgx-bundle/
# caller outputs that may contain individual-level calls
**/results.zip
**/*-variants.zip
**/per_individual*
# secrets / tokens
*.token
*token*.json
rclone.conf
.config/rclone/
